Package com.rays.bean

Class FollowUpBean

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.rays.bean.BaseBean
      • com.rays.bean.FollowUpBean
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DropdownListBean
    public class FollowUpBean
extends BaseBean
    Bean class representing a follow-up appointment between a patient and a doctor. Extends BaseBean. Contains patient and doctor details along with visit date and fees. author Aastik Sahu
